Class Configuration

java.lang.Object
com.stripe.model.StripeObject
com.stripe.net.ApiResource
com.stripe.model.billingportal.Configuration
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasId, MetadataStore<Configuration>, StripeActiveObject, StripeObjectInterface
public class Configuration extends ApiResource implements HasId, MetadataStore<Configuration>
A portal configuration describes the functionality and behavior you embed in a portal session. Related guide: Configure the customer portal.
